name: Member Pronoun Distribution
query:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN pronouns IS NULL OR pronouns = '' OR TRIM(pronouns) = '' 
    THEN 'Unknown' 
    ELSE pronouns 
  END as pronouns,
  COUNT(*) as count
FROM `tabMember` 
WHERE status IN ('Active', 'Dues Outstanding')
GROUP BY pronouns
ORDER BY count DESC
